@startuml
title Ott Based System Mini Reel - State Transition Diagram

initial : Initial State

state "Logged Out" {
    state "Create Account"
    state "Watch Videos"
}

state "Logged In" {
    state "Upload Videos"
    state "Save Video to Likes List"
    state "View Saved Videos"
    state "Enter Discussion"
}

:User creates an account; -> Create Account
:User watches videos; -> Watch Videos
:User uploads a video; -> Upload Videos
:User saves a video in likes list; -> Save Video to Likes List
:User views saved videos from likes list; -> View Saved Videos
:User enters discussion option; -> Enter Discussion

Logged Out --> Create Account : Start
Create Account --> Watch Videos : Login
Watch Videos --> Logged In : Login
Logged In --> Upload Videos : Upload
Logged In --> Save Video to Likes List : Like
Save Video to Likes List --> Logged In : View
Logged In --> View Saved Videos : View Likes
Logged In --> Enter Discussion : Discuss

@enduml
